  <div id="div_term_input">
    <label id="label_term">Term:&nbsp</label>
    <input type="text" id="term" onKeyDown="onKeyDown()">
  </div>
  <br />

  <table id="results_partial">
    <tr>
      <p class="note">[Usage] Check "Semantic Tag" -> Type "Term" which you want to map [and Enter] -> The Closest terms of SNOMED CT will be displayed (Up to 20 terms)</p>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <p class="note">[Note 1] Available browser : Chrome, Safari</p>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <p class="note">[Note 2 to Chrome User] if you got  a CORS error, you need to install Chrome extension ("Allow-Control-Allow-Origin:*") at <a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/category/extensions">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/category/extensions</a></p>
    </tr>
  </table>

</body>
</html>
